column4: Below are the current list of HTTP methods supported by the Project Insight REST API. We currently support GET and POST and the occasional DELETE method. You can also search our Knowledgebase for tutorials\, release notes and other information about how Project Insight provides support for REST API. Please join us in the PI Forums to see what other developers have learned and shared. We are happy to provide guidance in the free forums or help you purchase API support hours.
